cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image retrieval and compression. It also involves machine learning techniques such as supervised learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Multimedia (cs.MM) and natural language processing (cs.CL) could also be possible sub-categories as the paper deals with semantic relationships and embeddings.
